&lt;p&gt;Since 2011, THE ICONIC has redefined the future of retail in Australia and New Zealand. As the #1 fashion e-commerce &amp;amp; lifestyle destination in the region, our e-commerce platforms provide an inspiring and seamless end-to-end customer experience through our own technology innovations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;prose max-w-full text-base leading-7 prose-li:my-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;THE ICONIC Commercial team sits at the heart of fashion, product and customer insight —blending data, trends and commercial smarts to shape what our customers see, love and shop next.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;prose max-w-full text-base leading-7 prose-li:my-0&quot;&gt;
