&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are currently looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Assistant Designer to join our own brand team.&lt;/strong&gt; Reporting into our Own Brand Buying Manager, this role is essential in driving &lt;/span&gt;the conception and development of all product in your allocated category by always driving innovation &amp;amp; creativity.&lt;/p&gt;
