&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understand and drive company wide strategies and OKR’s.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a close link with manufacturers to ensure seamless handover of developments, taking direct accountability for making sure all sample technical packs submitted are accurate, completed and submitted in line with set timeframes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate regularly with the Design Team to ensure any critical design issues or developments are highlighted and resolved when required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select, develop, and source fabrications, colours, trims etc. in line with company standards&lt;/li&gt;
